body.p: This is a purine metabolism model that is geared toward studies of gout.
The model is fully described in Curto et al., MBSC 151 (1998) pp 1-49
The model uses Generalized Mass Action (GMA;i.e. power law) descriptions of reaction rate laws.
Such descriptions are local approximations that assume independent substrate binding.
Default unit of substance redefined to micromole by comparison with the article. Nicolas Le Novere
Default unit of time redefined to minute by comparison with the article. Nicolas Le Novere
